        <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold mt-6">5. Troubleshooting and Pro Tips</h2>
        <ul class="list-disc pl-5 space-y-2">
          <li><strong>It Keeps Rapping</strong>: add "half-sung vocals" and "melodic storytelling", shorten lines, use tags. v4.5 is less prone.</li>
          <li><strong>Too Busy or Muddy</strong>: limit to 3 to 4 instruments; request "minimal arrangement".</li>
          <li><strong>Flat Chorus</strong>: add [stacked harmonies], [beat drop], and fills.</li>
          <li><strong>DnB Generic</strong>: specify "two-step break and reese bass", contrast half-time and full-time.</li>
          <li><strong>Voice Issues</strong>: generate sections separately; use thumbs down for bad takes. For non-English, phonetic lyrics help.</li>
          <li><strong>Workflow Hacks</strong>: use ChatGPT or Claude for lyrics or prompts. Analyze songs with AI for BPM or styles. Remix viral tracks.</li>
          <li><strong>Community Tips</strong>: from X and Reddit: simplify for AI (KISS method); use [Interlude] for instrumentals; thumbs up or down trains outputs.</li>
        </ul>

